  "description": "<h4>Application</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Compatible with 2015-2018 Ford Mustang GT 5.0L V8</li>\n  <li>For 5.0L V8 GT models only</li>\n  <li>Requires cutting the stock exhaust pipe</li>\n  <li>Using with aftermarket exhausts that are not 2.5\" will require additional parts or modifications</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Features</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Made of high-quality 16-gauge 409 Stainless Steel with computerized mandrel bends</li>\n  <li>Improves exhaust flow for an increase in overall performance</li>\n  <li>X crossover pipe design that adds a loud and raspy note; high-performance JDM racing design</li>\n  <li>Direct replacement to the stock resonated mid-pipe; weight reduced compared with stock resonated mid-pipe</li>\n  <li>Reuses stock catalytic converter; front ends necked down to fit stock catalytic converter; expanded and slit rear ends for slip-on fit to stock exhaust</li>\n  <li>All joints are TIG welded to prevent cracking and wear</li>\n  <li>100% brand new items, never used or installed</li>\n  <li>The accessories in the photos are included</li>\n  <li>1 year warranty for any manufacturing defect</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Technical Specifications</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Type: X-Pipe</li>\n  <li>Pipe Diameter: 2-1/2 in. (64mm)</li>\n  <li>Pipe Thickness: 16 gauge (1.5mm)</li>\n  <li>Material: 409 Stainless Steel</li>\n  <li>Finish: Natural</li>\n</ul>\n",
